Time for a serious entry: the summers been okay because I've been able to see gabrielle through most of it- I haven't practiced much art recently, but I'll be getting on that- I need to work less in the realm of nude art and more with conceptual and candid such works- I need models, sadly, I have no friends so no one really reads this :( so it would be foolish to make a call for them, and Im far to cheap to go to boston or to hire ones around here (especially considering the people around here are stupid and annoying for the most part. It seems to be a new trend to not answer me when i talk to you over the internet, be it over aim or livejournal, or myspace, or whatever... it really gets on my nerves, this is the whole reason i have such few friends- it's because no one is genuine, which really gets to me. All I've been doing recently is getting angry over stupid artwork, saying i need a job, and playing Guitar Hero (<3). Yesterday I got incredibly angry over nothing (Seriously, nothing) and Gabrielle thinks i was mad at her, which i wasn't. Perhaps i should get a perscription for those chill pills i hear so much about




Seriously, though, should I cut my hair?

I'm going to make a serious entry, I swear. So I'm having issues with the demon that calls herself my mother, and every time i come home, i feel as if im going to have a nervous breakdown- shes a miserable awful woman. And this whole apartment thing is crashing down because of her. At least i'll be living with gabrielle, which is the #1 stress and pain reliever in america, as said by the FDA. Most of my work is caught up, i just need to build a stupid form study thing for next wednesday, but that shouldnt be too hard. Then i have my final for government which is going to be a six page paper, which once again shouldnt be too bad, and my final for art history is already complete (i think i passed). as for drawing, im doing a series of photographs inspired by andy worhol, ill need a couple male and female nude models, but i know 3 who are willing, but ill need a male and one more female. and my visual language final is pivitol on gabrielle that she gets the html completed for me, so that i may continue making the website. after that, school will be over, which scares me, because ill have to be in this hell hole for the rest of the summer; hopefully ill get a job, so i can... you know, live. I went to best buy with the coolest AZN ever (Joy) and i got an XBOX 360 live-strong braclet, suprisingly, it isnt HUEG. The summer is going to be awful, i cant wait until i can live with gabrielle, and no one is going to get in my way and stop me. i really hate people who get off really well and do nothing for it, but people who did nothing wrong and work their asses off are raped just because of circumstance. 

by the way, if you need any photography done for you, I'm lowering my prices, and also, ive gotten a lot better, so tell me when, ok?
got my apartment, will be living with gabrielle on wait street. its a nice big studio so come visit me next year
